Goal:
Test synchronization of monitor with FCC.
(Note: Derivative test rtlmin_2566_chicken runs with "+min_frontend_clock_gate_disable=1".) 

Details:
TEST IDEA:
There are 8 minions:
  - thread 1 is doing long operations (accesses to L3, div, uncacheds);
  - thread 0 wait for FCC, do a load/store in L2 in some shared data, and increment FCC for the next minion t0;

 All minions have thread1 running, and only minion 0 has thread0 awake (other minions will be waken up by minion-1).

